	<td>Kolodyazhnaya, M., Zvyagina, G., Bilych, I., Zhekov, K., Kharchenko, N. and Fil, V.</td>
	<td>Is LiCoPO4 a pyroelectric? <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Kolodyazhnaya20171240','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Kolodyazhnaya20171240','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
