	<td>Piezoelectric response in SmFe3(BO3)4, a non-piezoactive configuration. The surface piezoelectric effect <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Kolodyazhnaya2017924','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Kolodyazhnaya2017924','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
