	<td>Role of acoustic phonons in the negative thermal expansion of layered structures and nanotubes based on them <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Eremenko2016401','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Eremenko2016401','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
