	<td>Effect of step-edge on spectral properties and planar stability of metallic bigraphene <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Eremenko201699','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Eremenko201699','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
