	<td>Growth and characterization of large CeAlO<sub>3</sub> perovskite crystals <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Arhipov2015116','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Arhipov2015116','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
