	<td>Electronic structure and exchange interactions in GdB4 <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Baranovskiy201596','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Baranovskiy201596','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
