	<td>The Magnetic Properties of Single Crystal SrCo2Ti2Fe8O19 Compound <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Mihalik2015259','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Mihalik2015259','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
