	<td>Zvyagina, G.</td>
	<td>Magnetoelastic properties of Nd<sub>0.9</sub>Dy<sub>0.1</sub>Fe<sub>3</sub>(BO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>4</sub> ferroborate <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Zvyagina2014454','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Zvyagina2014454','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
