	<td>Acoustic characteristics of FeSe single crystals <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Zvyagina2013','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Zvyagina2013','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
