	<td>Structural first-order transformation in La 2/3Ba 1/3MnO 3: ESR study <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Polishchuk20124225','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Polishchuk20124225','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
