	<td>Grechnev, G., Logosha, A., Panfilov, A., Kuchin, A. and Vasijev, A.</td>
	<td>Effect of pressure on the magnetic properties of YNi5, LaNi5, and CeNi5 <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Grechnev2011138','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Grechnev2011138','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
	<td>2011</td>
	<td><font color="#006400">Low Temperature Physics</font><br/>Vol. 37(2), pp. 138-143&nbsp;</td>
