	<td>Magnetic anisotropy in 2H-NbSe2 electron irradiated single crystals <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Bartolomé2009470','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Bartolomé2009470','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
