	<td>Low-temperature phase segregation in La2/3 Ba1/3 Mn O3: Manifestation of nonequilibrium thermodynamics <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Beznosov2009449','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Beznosov2009449','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
