	<td>Electron doping of Nb Se2 <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Eremenko2009430','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Eremenko2009430','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
