	<td>Low temperature heat capacity of Nd2/3Ca1/3MnO 3 and (Nd0.9 Y0.1)2/3Ca1/3MnO 3 manganites: Transformation of the Schottky-like anomaly <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Fertman2009','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Fertman2009','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
	<td>2009</td>
	<td><font color="#006400">Journal of Physics: Conference Series</font><br/>Vol. 150(4), pp. 042031&nbsp;</td>
