	<td>Electronic structure and magnetic properties of transition metal diborides <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Grechnev200975','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Grechnev200975','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
