	<td>Raman scattering study of a two-dimensional S = 1 quantum spin system Ni5(TeO3)4Cl2 <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Peschanskii2009196','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Peschanskii2009196','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
