	<td>Quasi-exactly solvable models based on special functions <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Dolya2008','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Dolya2008','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
