	<td>Kontrym-Sznajd, G., Samsel-Czekała, M., Grechnev, G. and Sormann, H.</td>
	<td>Fermi surface of ErGa3 <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Kontrym-Sznajd20073879','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Kontrym-Sznajd20073879','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
