	<td>Influence of magnetic field on the paramagnetic-ferromagnetic transition in a La1-x Cax Mn O3 (x≈0.25) crystal: Ultrasonic and transport studies <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Belevtsev2006','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Belevtsev2006','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
