	<td>Magnetic states and the crystal volume of Nd2/3Ca 1/3MnO3: Analysis of phase transformations <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Fertman2005787','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Fertman2005787','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
