	<td>Pinning in nomagnetic borocarbides <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Zholobenko20051043','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Zholobenko20051043','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
