	<td>Anomalous diamagnetism in aluminum-lithium alloys <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Desnenko2004425','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Desnenko2004425','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
