	<td>Electronic structure and magnetic properties of GdM2 compounds <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Baranovskiy2003520','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Baranovskiy2003520','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
