	<td>Measurement of the densities of liquids and gases under pressure using magnetic levitation of a standard sample <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Panfilov2002789','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Panfilov2002789','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
