	<td>A general approach to potentials with two known levels <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Dolya20011981','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Dolya20011981','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
