	<td>Magnetovolume effect in YbAgCu4 <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Svechkarev20012144141','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Svechkarev20012144141','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
