	<td>Direct observation of a manifestation of magnetoelastic coupling in a low-dimensional virtual ferroelastic <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Zvyagina2000354','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Zvyagina2000354','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
