	<td>Superconductivity effects in hopping conductivity of single-crystal La2CuO4 with excess oxygen <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Belevtsev19971223','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Belevtsev19971223','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
