	<td>Fil, V., Gaiduk, A., Kolobov, I., Ignatovaa, T., Fil, D., Barilo, S. and Zhigunov, D.</td>
	<td>Magnetoelastic effects in Nd2CuO4 single crystals <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Fil19962153','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Fil19962153','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
