	<td>Low-temperature magnetic properties of terbium orthoferrite single crystals <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Guretskii1996897','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Guretskii1996897','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
