<tr id="Grechnev1994835" class="entry">
	<td>Grechnev, G., Jarlborg, T., Panfilov, A., Peter, M. and Svechkarev, I.</td>
	<td>The effect of pressure on the electronic structure and magnetic susceptibility of ε-FeSi <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Grechnev1994835','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Grechnev1994835','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
