	<td>Zero sound in normal and superconducting molybdenum <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Bezuglyi19917867','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Bezuglyi19917867','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
