	<td>Effect of pressure on the magnetic susceptibility of transition metals <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Svechkarev198935','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Svechkarev198935','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
