	<td>Magnetostriction of antiferromagnetic FeGe2 <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Franus-Muir1984615','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Franus-Muir1984615','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
