	<td>Magnetostriction of dilute hydrogenated palladium-rhodium alloys <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Pluzhnikov19842411','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Pluzhnikov19842411','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
