	<td>Nonlinear absorption of sound in superconductors <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Fil1976733','abstract')">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Fil1976733','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]</p></td>
